> Anyone know for sure if they are still saying that they will finish the shawl quests?  There was a thread up a while ago about uncompleted quests that I believe someone from VI was watching, but I was unable to read it to see if the coldain shawl quest was mentioned in the thread.<br>
<br>
The quest does not end, but after step 7 it asks you to keep checking back for more information, but so far (almost a year later) there is still no 8th-10th step(s).<br>
<br>
Would be great if VI could finish with this quest they started as I would like to add to the challenge that the first 7 (or maybe just 5-6-7) were.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushakwontriton.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ShakwonTriton</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/02 10:23:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4515.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain Sawl 8??  Going to be implemented?</span><hr size=1> Supposedly after luclin came out and was &quot;stable&quot; they would implement the next steps, Ive been checking every patch and still no luck =( <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upetercorbin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>petercorbin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/02 12:37:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4515.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain Sawl 8??  Going to be implemented?</span><hr size=1> All i have to say is they better put in the last 3 shawl quests before they put all their effort into Planes of Power.. my coldain faction has been in a holding pattern waiting for these to come out and i'm getting really thirsty for coldain blood.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucolossusa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Colossusa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/02 7:12:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4515.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain Sawl 8??  Going to be implemented?</span><hr size=1> I heard the shawl quests were made by Kendrick of the Safehouse...Yes this place.<br>
