 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvaslin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vaslin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Head Safehouse Admin</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/25/02 12:33:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4515.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain Sawl 8??  Going to be implemented?</span><hr size=1> &gt; I heard the shawl quests were made by Kendrick of the Safehouse...Yes this place.<br>
<br>
